00:59:00,330 --> 00:59:02,957
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(WISP CALLING)</font></b>

968
00:59:13,384 --> 00:59:15,178
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#808080">MERIDA:</font></b> Mum, look.

969
00:59:22,018 --> 00:59:23,244
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(WIND WHISTLES)</font></b>

970
00:59:23,269 --> 00:59:25,205
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(ELINOR BEAR GROANS)</font></b>

971
00:59:25,230 --> 00:59:27,815
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#808080">MERIDA:</font></b> Why did the
wisps bring us here?

972
00:59:27,941 --> 00:59:29,442
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(ELINOR BEAR MOANS)</font></b>

973
00:59:34,614 --> 00:59:36,658
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(ELINOR BEAR HUFFS AND SNORTS)</font></b>

974
00:59:54,926 --> 00:59:57,403
